{
  "texts": [
    "DiscussionTo understand how the public universities in Hong Kong respond to the emergence of ChatGPT, this article divided the timeline into three phases, which are procrastination, remediation, and adaptation.",
    "The first phase witnessed most universities not taking a stance toward ChatGPT.",
    "While many universities have only been setting up working groups to discuss this matter at that time, HKU and LU have been good examples of making a \"temporary\" policy decision in a matter of urgency.",
    "These two early responders in Hong Kong public universities in general issued policies within two months of ChatGPT's launch, which is consistent with the findings of Xiao et al. [56].",
    "However, it was still in the middle of the second semester in which students were about to do and submit their assignments."
  ]
}